## relativeSpatialPosition - Formal Specification

### 1. ODRL Definition

```turtle
:relativeSpatialPosition
    a :LeftOperand, owl:NamedIndividual, skos:Concept ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy odrl: ;
    skos:broader :relativePosition ;
    rdfs:label "Relative Spatial Asset Position"@en ;
    skos:definition "The relative spatial positions - expressed as percentages 
                     of full values - of four corners of a rectangle on a 
                     2D-canvas or the eight corners of a cuboid in a 3D-space 
                     of the target Asset."@en ;
    skos:note "See also Absolute Spatial Asset Position."@en ;
    skos:scopeNote "Non-Normative"@en .
```

