### 4. Domain Specification

$$\text{dom}(\texttt{relativeSpatialPosition}) = [0, 100]$$

| Property | Value | Justification |
|----------|-------|---------------|
| **Lower bound** | 0 | Origin of canvas/space |
| **Upper bound** | 100 | Full extent of canvas/space |
| **Inclusive bounds** |  Both | 0% and 100% are valid positions |
| **Per-axis** | Yes | Each axis independently bounded |
| **1D treatment** | Sound over-approximation | For static conflict detection |

